[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/90/139091.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1264814","time":"2017-7-19 21:29","userId":"chaucerling","userName":"chaucer","userSign":"(あなたの傷は私の食べ物)","message":"不懂win10<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/21/62186.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1264824","time":"2017-7-19 21:42","userId":"epix","userName":"epix","userSign":"((((；ﾟДﾟ)))))))","message":"休眠就和关机一样... 恢复的时候从头开始引导吧","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/79/247930.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1264831","time":"2017-7-19 21:52","userId":"cuiyn","userName":"听风","userSign":"(好好生活，好好补番～)","message":"没啥不对劲的<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/14.gif\" smileid=\"53\" alt=\"(bgm37)\">休眠的官方解释是“保存会话并关闭计算机”，可能楼主想要的是睡眠<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>然后，关机之后再开机，我猜进入的首先是grub，倒计时结束后自动进elementary。<br>话说建议把Windows10的快速启动也关了，否则Linux系统可能不能操作Windows分区，因为快速启动貌似也是一种休眠<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/39/103988.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1264913","time":"2017-7-20 04:45","userId":"103988","userName":"·_﹙","userSign":"","message":"主要是担心会损坏系统或者是伤硬盘？毕竟折腾一次双系统重装感觉很麻烦+坑很多的样子<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>快速启动早就关了，倒是进入windows似乎还是挺快（因为没装什么乱七八糟的预启动软件吧），其实问这个问题还是因为elementaryos重启后似乎显示了出了啥错误，然后重启进windows卡得有点不正常。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/02/204.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1264855","time":"2017-7-19 22:43","userId":"mono","userName":"rnono","userSign":"(汝视视汝)","message":"win的休眠还是什么好像会导致uefi不启动linux","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/39/103988.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1264910","time":"2017-7-20 04:37","userId":"103988","userName":"·_﹙","userSign":"","message":"老掉牙的电脑连uefi都没……"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/77/127728.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1264865","time":"2017-7-19 23:18","userId":"chooperchang","userName":"海卫四","userSign":"(不要停！)","message":"13年装双系统时发现win8的休眠会在引导分区写入什么玩意，好像是uefi变量，关掉快速启动后才能稳定的用grub引导。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/39/103988.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1264911","time":"2017-7-20 04:40","userId":"103988","userName":"·_﹙","userSign":"","message":"开了快速启动连引导用的u盘都加载不了，然后引导用的u盘制作的时候，mac下什么软件做的都没法用，linux下的话似乎要用lilo写一下mbr，感觉好多坑……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/39/103988.jpg","floor":"#6-2","id":"1264912","time":"2017-7-20 04:40","userId":"103988","userName":"·_﹙","userSign":"","message":"不过这样说的话所以开了快速启动反而可以休眠唤醒还是windows么……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/74/37469.jpg","floor":"#6-3","id":"1265198","time":"2017-7-20 22:47","userId":"fantasy","userName":"fantasy","userSign":"","message":"不只是内存状态吗？<br>我总觉得休眠就是把内存写入硬盘，开机时把硬盘的内存状态读到内存里。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/77/127728.jpg","floor":"#6-4","id":"1265206","time":"2017-7-21 00:32","userId":"chooperchang","userName":"海卫四","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">fantasy</span> 说: 不只是内存状态吗？<br>我总觉得休眠就是把内存写入硬盘，开机时把硬盘的内存状态读到内存里。</q></div>不是，内存写入硬盘的一个区域，然后在引导分区写入内存被存入的位置吧，我没在引导分区找到别的文件但是efi变量显然被改动了。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/74/37469.jpg","floor":"#6-5","id":"1265224","time":"2017-7-21 07:33","userId":"fantasy","userName":"fantasy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">海卫四</span> 说: 不是，内存写入硬盘的一个区域，然后在引导分区写入内存被存入的位置吧，我没在引导分区找到别的文件但是efi变量显然被改动了。</q></div>efi被改动，很奇怪。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/80/178081.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1264960","time":"2017-7-20 09:29","userId":"ershiwo","userName":"板砖加身","userSign":"(大破的那珂酱好萌！)","message":"不要用 wbm 引导，换 grub2。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/74/37469.jpg","floor":"#7-1","id":"1265197","time":"2017-7-20 22:46","userId":"fantasy","userName":"fantasy","userSign":"","message":"看样子并不是wbm，确实是grub引导啊？"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/15/341586.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1265155","time":"2017-7-20 19:07","userId":"joenahm","userName":"张弗若","userSign":"(考前记一记，喝前摇一摇)","message":"哇 我也是这样搞得呢~~win10+eos 前几天还关不了机来着，这几天好了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/01.gif\" smileid=\"40\" alt=\"(bgm24)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/73/7320.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1265201","time":"2017-7-20 23:12","userId":"7320","userName":"HZ","userSign":"","message":"你试试在 /etc/default/grub 里加上 (或者修改) 这两行<br>GRUB_DEFAULT=saved<br>GRUB_SAVEDEFAULT=true<br>然后 update-grub.<br><br>上面两行是让 grub 记住每次启动时的选项，并作为下次启动的默认项。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/61/36176.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1265305","time":"2017-7-21 15:54","userId":"36176","userName":"豆沙包罐头","userSign":"(事到如今数不完了呀)","message":"elementary这个感觉比osx还要小清新啊","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/57/205716.jpg","floor":"#10-1","id":"1265376","time":"2017-7-21 20:16","userId":"zhudhjen","userName":"一只火龙果","userSign":"","message":"其实就是另一个 Linux 的发行版，对普通用户很友善的那种"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/39/103988.jpg","floor":"#10-2","id":"1265389","time":"2017-7-21 22:28","userId":"103988","userName":"·_﹙","userSign":"","message":"比较干净吧，osx现在感觉越来越臃肿了……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/61/36176.jpg","floor":"#10-3","id":"1265425","time":"2017-7-22 00:04","userId":"36176","userName":"豆沙包罐头","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">一只火龙果</span> 说: 其实就是另一个 Linux 的发行版，对普通用户很友善的那种</q></div>这个知道..之前有想搞个，后来手头没多余的机器就算了"}]}]